snippet: Theairra Taylor scored 21 points and made a go-ahead layup with 1:32 left as fifth-seeded and No. 23-ranked Iowa held on for a 77-73 win over eighth-seeded Ohio State on Saturday in the semifinals of the Big Ten tournament....

headline.print_headline: No. 23 Iowa Tops Ohio St. 77-73 in Big Ten Semis
headline.main: No. 23 Iowa Tops Ohio St. 77-73 in Big Ten Semis

lead_paragraph: Theairra Taylor scored 21 points and made a go-ahead layup with 1:32 left as fifth-seeded and No. 23-ranked Iowa held on for a 77-73 win over eighth-seeded Ohio State on Saturday in the semifinals of the Big Ten tournament.
